    "custom_liquid_FNNt3i": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Gagnant",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<section class=\"tb-winner\">\n  <div class=\"tb-winner__inner\">\n\n    <!-- Badge -->\n    <div class=\"tb-winner__badge\">\n      <span class=\"tb-winner__medal\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 40 40\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <circle cx=\"20\" cy=\"20\" r=\"10\" fill=\"#e7c06a\"/>\n          <path d=\"M20 14l2 4 4 .6-3 2.6.8 4-3.8-2-3.8 2 .8-4-3-2.6 4-.6 2-4z\" fill=\"#8b6511\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </span>\n      <span class=\"tb-winner__badge-text\">GAGNANT DU COMPARATIF</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Logo -->\n    <div class=\"tb-winner__logo\">\n      <img\n        src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0903/1342/5220/files/logo_horizontal_blanc_9f782eb1-ab3e-493d-9abb-43b8b960f501.svg?v=1762799224\"\n        alt=\"Tediber\"\n        loading=\"lazy\">\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Title -->\n    <h2 class=\"tb-winner__title\">\n      LE MATELAS HYBRIDE PREMIUM<br>\n      TEDIBER GAGNE LE MATCH\n    </h2>\n\n    <!-- Arguments -->\n    <div class=\"tb-winner__points\">\n\n      <div class=\"tb-winner__point\">\n        <span class=\"tb-winner__check\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n            <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle>\n            <path d=\"M10.4 15.6 7.7 12.9a1 1 0 1 1 1.4-1.4l1.7 1.7 4.2-4.2a1 1 0 0 1 1.4 1.4l-5 5a1 1 0 0 1-1.4 0Z\" fill=\"#ffffff\"></path>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n        <p>\n          Maintien du dos renforcé et soutien plus précis grâce à sa structure de couches de confort supérieure et à sa densité de ressorts plus élevée.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tb-winner__point\">\n        <span class=\"tb-winner__check\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n            <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle>\n            <path d=\"M10.4 15.6 7.7 12.9a1 1 0 1 1 1.4-1.4l1.7 1.7 4.2-4.2a1 1 0 0 1 1.4 1.4l-5 5a1 1 0 0 1-1.4 0Z\" fill=\"#ffffff\"></path>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n        <p>\n          Meilleure absorption des mouvements grâce à ses couches de mousse plus épaisses qui épousent le corps et à sa structure de ressorts ensachés répartis en 5 zones de confort.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tb-winner__point\">\n        <span class=\"tb-winner__check\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n            <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle>\n            <path d=\"M10.4 15.6 7.7 12.9a1 1 0 1 1 1.4-1.4l1.7 1.7 4.2-4.2a1 1 0 0 1 1.4 1.4l-5 5a1 1 0 0 1-1.4 0Z\" fill=\"#ffffff\"></path>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n        <p>\n          Plus de personnalisation du confort grâce au surmatelas réversible qui permet de choisir sa sensation d’accueil selon ses préférences.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n <div class=\"tb-winner__point\">\n        <span class=\"tb-winner__check\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n            <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle>\n            <path d=\"M10.4 15.6 7.7 12.9a1 1 0 1 1 1.4-1.4l1.7 1.7 4.2-4.2a1 1 0 0 1 1.4 1.4l-5 5a1 1 0 0 1-1.4 0Z\" fill=\"#ffffff\"></path>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n        <p>\n          Garantie d’un confort longue durée grâce à une production française et un savoir-faire de plus de 10 ans.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- CTA (seul élément cliquable) -->\n    <div class=\"tb-winner__cta-wrap\">\n      <a class=\"tb-winner__cta\" href=\"https://www.tediber.com/products/matelas-hybride-premium\">\n        Découvrir le matelas Hybride Premium\n      </a>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Trust -->\n    <div class=\"tb-winner__trust\">\n      100 nuits d’essai <span class=\"tb-winner__sep\">|</span> Livraison sous 48h\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <style>\n    .tb-winner{\n      background:#F1DDC5;\n      padding:36px 16px 40px;\n      overflow:hidden;\n    }\n\n    .tb-winner__inner{\n      max-width:760px;\n      margin:0 auto;\n      text-align:center;\n    }\n\n    /* Badge */\n    .tb-winner__badge{\n      display:inline-flex;\n      align-items:center;\n      gap:8px;\n      background:#06173a;\n      color:#fff;\n      padding:8px 14px;\n      border-radius:8px;\n      border:2px solid #e7c06a;\n      font-size:12px;\n      font-weight:800;\n      letter-spacing:.02em;\n    }\n\n    .tb-winner__medal{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;line-height:0;}\n\n    /* Logo */\n    .tb-winner__logo{ margin:20px 0 12px; }\n    .tb-winner__logo img{ width:140px; height:auto; display:block; margin:0 auto; }\n\n    /* Title */\n    .tb-winner__title{\n      font-family:\"Obviously Narrow\",\"Obviously\",system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;\n      font-weight:900;\n      font-size:28px;\n      line-height:1.05;\n      margin:12px 0 20px;\n      color:#06173a;\n      text-transform:uppercase;\n      letter-spacing:.01em;\n    }\n\n    /* Points */\n    .tb-winner__points{\n      display:flex;\n      flex-direction:column;\n      gap:18px;\n      margin-bottom:24px;\n    }\n\n    .tb-winner__point{\n      display:flex;\n      gap:12px;\n      text-align:left;\n      align-items:flex-start;\n    }\n\n    .tb-winner__point p{\n      font-size:14px;\n      line-height:1.35;\n      margin:0;\n      color:#06173a;\n      font-weight:500;\n    }\n\n    /* ✅ EXACTEMENT le style de coche utilisé dans tes sections précédentes */\n    .tb-winner__check{\n      color:#1f7a55; /* cercle via currentColor */\n      display:inline-flex;\n      width:24px;\n      height:24px;\n      align-items:center;\n      justify-content:center;\n      transform:translateY(2px);\n      flex:0 0 auto;\n    }\n\n    /* CTA */\n    .tb-winner__cta-wrap{ margin:22px 0 18px; }\n    .tb-winner__cta{\n      display:block;\n      background:#06173a;\n      color:#fff;\n      text-decoration:none;\n      padding:16px 18px;\n      border-radius:8px;\n      font-weight:800;\n      font-size:14px;\n      font-family:\"Obviously Narrow\",\"Obviously\",system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;\n    }\n\n    /* Trust */\n    .tb-winner__trust{\n      font-size:13px;\n      color:#06173a;\n      font-weight:600;\n    }\n    .tb-winner__sep{ margin:0 8px; }\n\n    @media (min-width:768px){\n      .tb-winner{ padding:56px 40px; }\n      .tb-winner__title{ font-size:36px; }\n      .tb-winner__point p{ font-size:15px; }\n      .tb-winner__cta{ max-width:420px; margin:0 auto; }\n    }\n  </style>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"tb-hybrid-for-you\">\n\n<div class=\"tb-hybrid-for-you__inner\">\n\n<h2 class=\"tb-hybrid-for-you__title\">\nLE MATELAS HYBRIDE PREMIUM<br>\nTEDIBER EST FAIT POUR<br>\nVOUS SI :\n</h2>\n\n<h3 class=\"tb-hybrid-for-you__subtitle\">\nVOUS SOUHAITEZ MIEUX DORMIR À deux<br>\n\n</h3>\n\n<p class=\"tb-hybrid-for-you__text\">Avec plus de 1 140 ressorts indépendants répartis en 5 zones de confort, le matelas Hybride Premium de Tediber assure une excellente absorption des mouvements, pour des nuits plus sereines à deux.\n</p>\n\n<h3 class=\"tb-hybrid-for-you__subtitle\">\nVous recherchez un MAINTIEN RENFORCÉ AU DOS\n</h3>\n\n<p class=\"tb-hybrid-for-you__text\">\nGrâce à sa composition de couches de mousse d’accueil, de soutien et de mémoire de forme haute densité, le matelas Hybride Premium de Tediber s’adapte à la morphologie de chaque dormeur et favorise un bon alignement de la colonne vertébrale toute la nuit.\n</p>\n\n<div class=\"tb-hybrid-for-you__highlight\">\n<span class=\"tb-hybrid-for-you__sparkle\">\n\n<svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\">\n<path d=\"M12 2l1.6 4.2L18 8l-4.4 1.8L12 14l-1.6-4.2L6 8l4.4-1.8L12 2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/>\n<path d=\"M19 14l.8 2 2 .8-2 .8-.8 2-.8-2-2-.8 2-.8.8-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/>\n</svg>\n\n</span>\n\n<p>\nVous vous êtes reconnus ? <strong>Alors n'attendez plus !</strong>\n</p>\n\n</div>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.tediber.com/products/matelas-hybride-premium\" class=\"tb-hybrid-for-you__cta\">\nDécouvrir le matelas Hybride Premium\n</a>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you{\nbackground:#ffffff;\npadding:36px 16px 40px;\n}\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you__inner{\nmax-width:760px;\nmargin:0 auto;\n}\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you__title{\nfont-family:\"Obviously Narrow\",\"Obviously\",system-ui;\nfont-weight:900;\nfont-size:28px;\nline-height:1.05;\ncolor:#06173a;\nmargin:0 0 18px 0;\ntext-transform:uppercase;\n}\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you__subtitle{\nfont-family:\"Obviously Narrow\",\"Obviously\",system-ui;\nfont-weight:900;\nfont-size:18px;\nline-height:1.15;\ncolor:#06173a;\nmargin:26px 0 10px 0;\ntext-transform:uppercase;\n}\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you__text{\nfont-size:14px;\nline-height:1.45;\ncolor:#06173a;\nmargin:0;\n}\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you__text strong{\nfont-weight:800;\n}\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you__highlight{\ndisplay:flex;\nalign-items:center;\ngap:10px;\nmargin:26px 0 20px;\ncolor:#06173a;\nfont-size:14px;\n}\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you__sparkle{\ndisplay:flex;\nalign-items:center;\njustify-content:center;\ncolor:#06173a;\n}\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you__highlight p{\nmargin:0;\n}\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you__cta{\ndisplay:block;\nbackground:#06173a;\ncolor:#fff;\ntext-decoration:none;\ntext-align:center;\npadding:16px;\nborder-radius:8px;\nfont-weight:800;\nfont-size:14px;\n}\n\n@media (min-width:768px){\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you{\npadding:56px 40px;\n}\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you__title{\nfont-size:36px;\n}\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you__subtitle{\nfont-size:22px;\n}\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you__text{\nfont-size:15px;\n}\n\n.tb-hybrid-for-you__cta{\nmax-width:420px;\nmargin:0 auto;\n}\n\n}\n\n</style>\n\n</section>",
